Fehérvárcsurgó

Fehérvárcsurgó is a city in Fejér County, in Hungary.

GPS Coordinates of Fehérvárcsurgó, Fejér County, Hungary

Fehérvárcsurgó is located on the latitude of 47.29349 and longitude of 18.2646 and has a geohash of u2kvp9ebs18b.

Cities and Towns near Fehérvárcsurgó

The nearest significant population center from Fehérvárcsurgó is Kincsesbánya in Fejér County, Hungary, located 3 kilometers or 2 miles ↘ SE of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Bodajk (Fejér County, Hungary) located 4 km (2 mi) ↖ NW and Móri Járás (Fejér County, Hungary) located 7 km (4 mi) ↖ NW of Fehérvárcsurgó.
